00:46:05.180 --> 00:46:10.820
course i'm going to add this support and of course i'm going to add this feature and it just grew and

00:46:10.820 --> 00:46:15.540
grew and grew and grew and apparently i just hit a nerve so this was utterly unplanned this was

00:46:15.740 --> 00:46:23.620
never my intention at all and uh i just wanted to solve my own problem and have continued to solve

00:46:23.780 --> 00:46:29.360
