00:51:45.800 --> 00:51:52.680
I always say that the main advice I give is just to focus on a problem that is important to you.

00:51:53.680 --> 00:52:00.240
More than, you know, like innovation, market disruption or whatever, just like focus on a problem that is actually important to you.

00:52:00.660 --> 00:52:02.760
