00:52:11.860 --> 00:52:18.880
And then try to solve it and then use that as the guide of what to do, what to learn, what to focus on, what to do.

00:52:19.260 --> 00:52:22.780
In many cases, it's just learning a framework that is already there.

00:52:23.050 --> 00:52:29.540
